python ai/train.py --orchestrate --rewards-config default

# Use simplified rewards for faster learning  
python ai/train.py --orchestrate --rewards-config simplified

# Use balanced intermediate rewards
python ai/train.py --orchestrate --rewards-config balanced
```

### Progressive Reward Training Strategy

```bash
