```

**Key Features:**
- **Load Balancing:** Uses 50% of CPU cores (max 4 concurrent sessions)
- **Progress Tracking:** Shows slowest agent progress across all sessions
- **Automatic Scaling:** Handles 2-6 agents with balanced matchups

**Orchestration Metrics:**
```
