```

### Selective Replay System

**Episode Tracking:**
```python
class SelectiveEpisodeTracker:
    # Automatically tracks during training:
    # - Best reward episode
    # - Worst reward episode  
    # - Shortest episode (fastest win)
```

**Replay File Generation:**
```
ai/event_log/
├── replay_Agent_vs_Bot_best.json      # Highest reward episode
├── replay_Agent_vs_Bot_worst.json     # Lowest reward episode
