```

**Memory Management:**
- Keeps top 20 episode candidates during training
- Prunes less interesting episodes automatically
- Saves only 3 most valuable replays per agent

### Training Phase System

**Progressive Training Phases:**
```bash
# Phase 1: Solo self-play for basic tactics
python ai/train.py --orchestrate --training-phase solo

# Phase 2: Cross-faction learning  
python ai/train.py --orchestrate --training-phase cross_faction

# Phase 3: Full composition complexity
